        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">How does automated tattoo aftercare work for studios?</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Tattoo aftercare automation sends clients a timed series of post-appointment emails with healing instructions, product recommendations, and check-in prompts — typically day 1, day 3, day 7, day 14, and day 30 post-session. InkFlow's aftercare module includes pre-written templates for different tattoo types (color, black-and-gray, cover-up, touch-up) with customizable branding. Automated follow-ups include a healed photo request at 30 days that feeds directly into the client's portfolio gallery. Studios using automated aftercare report 40% higher client retention rates compared to manual follow-up.</p>
